Debian: 
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/home/pberck/local/lib

Example:
--------

./configure --prefix=/home/pberck/local --with-timbl=/home/pberck/local
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/home/pberck/local/lib
